============================================
CHANGES MADE FROM ORIGINAL
============================================

1. Renamed plugin from Iris to KRUD World
2. Changed package from com.volmit.iris to dev.krud.world
3. Changed author to Krud Studio
4. Added Khmer Kingdom dimension (khmer-kingdom)
5. Added DonutSMP style messages
6. Added Asia/Phnom_Penh timezone support
7. Added KRUD branded config format
8. Added custom startup banner

